Patterned Adhesive Vinyl

(Click on images to see the various options in the series)

We offer a vast collection of patterned adhesive vinyl for all occasions.  If you are a fan of Oracal products, you will love this new line as the vinyl is from the same manufacturer and its characteristics quite similar. 

Each sheet is printed in our studio in Canada's National Capital Region using a professional eco-solvent process. We can also print custom images or designs for you as long as they are not copyrighted or protected against duplication.  

Please note that these are printed pictures; those with glitter or metallic appearances remain images and are not at all similar to our products containing glitter (e.g. ultra metallic, transparent glitter) or our chrome adhesive vinyls.

This vinyl is outdoor durable for up to 3 years and may be used on projects just like your regular Oracal or other brands of non-patterned vinyl.  We do not recommend washing items to which it has been applied in the dishwasher.

Our patterned adhesive vinyl is compatible with all craft cutters such as: Cricut, Silhouette, Roland, GSS, Xyron, Craft ROBO, Graphtec, Quickutz, Inspirations, Pazzles, etc.

Use your regular transfer tape just like you would on non patterned vinyl.

About the Store

Your Canadian online source for adhesvie vinyls (Oracal 651 & 631, Styletech), Siser Heat Transfer Vinyl, patterned HTV and adhesive vinyls.  We also offer various blanks (clothing, sublimation etc.)

Our goal is to offer crafters and small businesses the full spectrum of colours and size options, amazing prices and service beyond your expectations.
